{"tid":699992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1.2公里外睇見你打乞嗤 杜克大學研發 十億像素超級相機落入中國手中","createTime":"2018-06-13T03:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T10:35:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"056da1d926ecc560caa0b1a796db2ed39ffa1a5a","tid":699992,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:38:55.000Z","msg":"片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/video/china/3DD9C94D-2847-47E9-9F92-C870CCAD5CEF.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fvideo%2Fchina%2F3DD9C94D-2847-47E9-9F92-C870CCAD5CEF.html&d=FVhtRRrTkXeh5v7gDiq%2B69r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=799cc24b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/video/china/3DD9C94D-2847-47E9-9F92-C870CCAD5CEF.html</a><br />\n<br />\n這種監控器能在1.2公里外睇見你打乞嗤<br />\n搭載了19個鏡頭的Mantis是世界上最強大的監控器之一。將其安裝在市區高樓樓頂，它能夠對大範圍內的人和物進行監視，甚至能辨別一些微小的細節，比如1.2公里外的人打了個乞嗤。如今，這種監控器加入了中國龐大的監控網絡。封面圖片來源：Qilai Shen for The Wall Street Journal<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n杜克大學研發的十億像素超級相機如何落入中國手中？<br />\n五年前，杜克大學的一個科學家團隊利用美國國防部的贊助開發了一款開創性的十億級像素相機，而在2016年該項目首席研究員David Brady移居中國開啟他的業務之後，這項從未被美國政府採用的技術正被中國警方使用......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/CT-TEC-20180612123012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2FCT-TEC-20180612123012&d=FVhtRRrTkXeh5v7gDiq%2B69r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8e16a6a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/CT-TEC-20180612123012</a>"},{"pid":"970d83c6f96d6e4be262661d65901421f7540c85","tid":699992,"uid":57410,"like":2,"dislike":30,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:42:42.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正怕咩？"},{"pid":"bbf5ba53bdae7a198c7dfa41c0a5e6744281db3a","tid":699992,"uid":48083,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"970d83c6f96d6e4be262661d65901421f7540c85","tid":699992,"uid":57410,"like":2,"dislike":30,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:42:42.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正怕咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:43:33.000Z","msg":"你真名係咩?"},{"pid":"02b986